 "data": "@startmindmap
* Machine Learning Engineer
** Computer Science Principles
*** Understand how programs run on computers (CPU, RAM, input/output devices).
*** Learn about binary representation and data storage.
** Level 1 Coding Tutorials
*** Get hands-on experience with basic coding concepts.
*** Explore programming languages (Python, Java, etc.).
** Data Structures & Algorithms
*** Study fundamental data structures (arrays, linked lists, trees, etc.).
*** Learn about algorithm design and analysis.
** SQL Basics
*** Grasp the basics of SQL for data manipulation and querying.
** Numpy, Pandas, Data Visualization Libraries
*** Dive into Numpy and Pandas for data manipulation.
*** Explore data visualization tools (Matplotlib, Seaborn).
** Math, Statistics For Machine Learning
*** Understand essential math concepts (linear algebra, calculus).
*** Learn about statistical methods used in ML.
** Machine Learning
*** Explore supervised and unsupervised learning algorithms.
*** Understand model evaluation and hyperparameter tuning.
** Deep Learning
*** Study neural networks, backpropagation, and activation functions.
*** Explore deep learning frameworks (TensorFlow, PyTorch).
** ML Ops
*** Learn about deploying ML models in production.
*** Understand model monitoring and maintenance.
** Additional skills that will be helpful
*** Understanding principles of effective learning.
*** Collaborate through group study.
*** Maintain discipline and persistence.
** Useful Tips
@endmindmap
